    "Their proposed MPP model extends AViT to multi-physics settings by incorporating strategies for handling multi-channel inputs and system-specific normalization.",
    "In our parametric setting, such mechanisms are unnecessary.",
    "We adopt the same hyperparameter configuration as in table 8, which we found to yield the best results.",
    "AR-DiT Our autoregressive diffusion transformer follows the setup proposed in Kohl et al. (2024), where known frames are concatenated with noise and denoised progressively to generate the next physical state.",
    "As in (Rombach et al., 2022), we employ AdaLayerNorm to condition the model during the diffusion process."
